    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead">Staff and tutor guide for handling image files</span></p>
<div class="page">
<div class="section">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p>This guide includes:</p>
<ol>
<li>
<p>how to reduce the size of image files using Paint;</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>how to compress the size of an Office Document which includes images;</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>how to reduce the size of an Office Document which includes images by saving as PDF;</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>how to take a screenshot.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></Value>
